My Roles and Responsibilities:-
Review and analyze system specifications.
Collaborate with team to develop effective strategies and test plans.
Create and execute test cases (manual or automated) and analyze results.
Create logs to document testing phases and defects.
Report bugs and errors to development teams
Help troubleshoot issues.
Conduct post-release/ post-implementation testing.
Work with cross-functional teams to ensure quality throughout the software development lifecycle.
Logging and fixing the defects
As a part of team we are attending the Daily scrum call in that discuss with what did yesterdays and todays work Plan as well as sending the daily Status wise report to my team lead.
